Magic =
Using magic alongside the [[dragon claws]] will allow the player to kill the Mimic relatively quickly. High-levelled players should have little difficulty defeating the mimic with high-end gear.

The player should always use [[protect from melee]] and move around the room when the Mimic throws sweets, and the player should ignore the spawned [[Third Age minions]]. Protect from melee should be activated before the player enters the instance. The player should use stat-boosting potions and the ''invigorate'' option of the [[Imbued heart]] before entering the instance. The player should enter the fight in full melee gear and use both the dragon claws special attacks (can be substituted with a [[dragon dagger]] if the player does not have dragon claws).

